Name: Radline: Quarantine
About the game: Radline: Quarantine is a co-operative sandbox horde shooter set in a quarantined area infected by unknown virus. Key fetures: fast-paced online co-op up to 5 players customizable characters, rank system, unlockable items sentry turrets, tesla coils and other fancy zombie-killing stuff traps, barbed fences, barricades, buildable structures Team up with your friends and survive together!
